reviewText: Got this for my niece for christmas and she loves it. Her mom said she catches her playing it and practicing her moves all the time.
Title: Tinkerbell Dance Studio: Learn Ballet Step-By-Step

reviewText: Very good service and quick delivery.I rented this DVD at first to see what it is like.Well...I loved it!!!For the balanced quality of content which  is very bright,fun,joyfull  and professional at the same time.It is an actual ballet class in a fun but yet in real version.I purchased it as a present for my niece who wants to be a ballerina but doesn`t have a chance to join the studio yet.Besides all of the above DVD has 3 trailers that are fun to watch: ballet,hip-hop and jazz.
Title: Tinkerbell Dance Studio: Learn Ballet Step-By-Step

reviewText: She watches a bit then practices a few positions and learns their names.  It's great bit by bit for someone who loves to dance and is deciding whether she wants to attend a class or not.
Title: Tinkerbell Dance Studio: Learn Ballet Step-By-Step

reviewText: It is ok DVD. No problems with it, but it is not that great. I watch it with my daughter and it was a little boring (for me and for my 4 years old). It feels like something is missing.
Title: Tinkerbell Dance Studio: Learn Ballet Step-By-Step

reviewText: This is an ok video.  It's not the best for teaching ballet.  It's a little bit boring, I think.  My daughter was really excited about this at first, but only has done it two or three times.
Title: Tinkerbell Dance Studio: Learn Ballet Step-By-Step
